# open-questions, key-takeaways). Methodology writes to {cypilot_path}/.cache/explain/
# which resolves per project config. The legacy hardcoded `.cypilot/` directory
# is also ignored here so older runs do not pollute git status.
.cypilot/
**/.cache/explain/

